---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Get in touch with The Van Guide team. Submit corrections, pitch tips, claim a builder listing, or send press and partnership inquiries."
>
  <section class="container-read py-10 md:py-24">
    <div class="eyebrow mb-4">Contact</div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-tight mb-6">Get in touch.</h1>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Email <a href="mailto:hello@thevanguide.com">hello@thevanguide.com</a> for any of the following. Expect a response within a few business days.
      </p>
      <h2>Corrections</h2>
      <p>
        If something on this site is wrong, send the URL and the specific claim that needs fixing. Include a source if you have one. Corrections are taken seriously and acted on quickly.
      </p>
      <h2>Builder submissions</h2>
      <p>
        To submit a shop for the directory, send the business name, state, website, and which platforms they build on (Sprinter, ProMaster, Transit, etc.). Already listed? <a href="/builders/claim/">Claim your listing</a> to manage your profile.
      </p>
      <h2>Press and partnerships</h2>
      <p>
        Include your outlet or organization, your deadline, and what you're working on.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
